   617‚Üí
   618‚ÜíYou may pull in just the part of this semver utility that you need if you
   619‚Üíare sensitive to packing and tree-shaking concerns.  The main
   620‚Üí`require('semver')` export uses getter functions to lazily load the parts
   621‚Üíof the API that are used.
   622‚Üí
   623‚ÜíThe following modules are available:
   624‚Üí
